{"tid":394983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"平心而論，自殺呢件事本身係應該一視同仁咁哀悼","createTime":"2017-09-10T12:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T14:35:21.000Z","uid":46849,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21e97f0d00e1b2dcdb27d3b0693703968ee34ae0","tid":394983,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:18:12.000Z","msg":"我睇左 2 hours for a life 條片<br />\n同意你可以好憎某d 人<br />\n但唔應該畀呢d 嘢轉移視線<br />\n至少呢兩日仲有其他人跳樓自殺<br />\n個焦點係應該放返入去自殺者身上<br />\n<br />\n條片︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/agentofchangehk/videos/755760611298472/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fagentofchangehk%2Fvideos%2F755760611298472%2F&d=pHA8xSnmiKajWaFOQZ69K54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3dbea381\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/agentofchangehk/videos/755760611298472/</a><br />\n<br />\n我認同至少要有個信念，幫返自己朋友<br />\n始終無論教育制度點搞<br />\n最終可以陪到你一世既其實都係你老友<br />\n唔係d 狗官<br />\n<br />\n其他人雙重標準，唔代表我都要搬龍門<br />\n<br />\nSOR 認真左，有感而發"},{"pid":"83ab3966a2acbcb6d98bad2ba4fb6a6ffd3892c3","tid":394983,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:19:52.000Z","msg":"我地係nobody"},{"pid":"affae0f48b28943f8c9fb16ad85ed711d80db3c6","tid":394983,"uid":46849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:31:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我地係nobody</blockquote><br />\n正正因為咁<br />\n<br />\n先要自己振作自救"},{"pid":"0249b5a774968e470e8de534ad56519fb68bbf12","tid":394983,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我地係nobody</blockquote><br />\n正正因為咁<br />\n<br />\n先要自己振作自救</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點自救？"},{"pid":"09155a93dc8af9aa45b721977b8c866b022688e0","tid":394983,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T13:00:27.000Z","msg":"希特拉都係自殺<br />\n你哀唔哀悼？"},{"pid":"ea7b62b61e2e86ed5858db519ab85e46cd664b33","tid":394983,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,